Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles.

09:46.953 --> 09:51.758 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Still to come on the "NewsHour":
rising tensions in the South
China Sea; upgrades to U.S.
nuclear

09:51.758 --> 09:56.329 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
