co-founded by designer Miguel

35:47.479 --> 35:51.583 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
McKelvey in 2010.

35:51.583 --> 35:57.222 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The thinking was that, given the
swelling ranks of the
self-employed, why not lease

35:57.222 --> 36:03.495 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
