amenities and camaraderie to
attract contingent workers?

36:09.067 --> 36:12.303 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MIGUEL MCKELVEY, Co-Founder,
WeWork: If we unite them
together, bring them together,

36:12.303 --> 36:15.907 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
