work and life.

36:19.177 --> 36:24.449 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
PAUL SOLMAN: Plus, it gives them
a legal address for mail and the
like, an instant network

36:24.449 --> 36:31.389 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
