enough pool of people to buy
into group health care plans.

36:31.389 --> 36:36.261 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
McKelvey's is the sunny spin on
housing the
free-to-be-you-and-me work
force. But Brooklyn

36:36.261 --> 36:41.232 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
