work, benefit-free.

37:06.491 --> 37:12.464 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
RICHARD GREENWALD: I'm
hard-pressed to see a sector of
the economy where outsourcing

37:12.464 --> 37:20.305 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
