this, but they're the good kind.
It's everyone working.

37:56.674 --> 38:02.147 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
It's coffee and spa water on
draft, beer after 5:00. It's a
good space to feel energetic

38:02.147 --> 38:06.584 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
and inspired to get work done.

38:06.584 --> 38:11.689 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PAUL SOLMAN: Am I being too
negative to think that what
you're doing is providing
community

38:11.689 --> 38:18.663 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
