be lonely, as opposed to
inspiring people and giving

38:18.663 --> 38:23.735 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
them meaning, whereas they
couldn't come up with meaning on
their own?

38:23.735 --> 38:30.975 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
MIGUEL MCKELVEY: Well,
certainly, there's components of
both of those things, but as

38:30.975 --> 38:38.750 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
an entrepreneur who had spent
time working at home, I could
have all the ideas in my

38:38.750 --> 38:43.588 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
