that with, where does it go?

38:46.824 --> 38:50.662 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
PAUL SOLMAN: So, WeWork chose
spaces to maximize mingling.

38:50.662 --> 38:53.765 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MIGUEL MCKELVEY: Most of our
buildings are on corners. We
choose buildings that have

38:53.765 --> 38:57.702 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
