makes people feel good.

38:57.702 --> 39:01.606 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
PAUL SOLMAN: And then McKelvey
designed the spaces to further
spur interaction.

39:01.606 --> 39:07.712 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MIGUEL MCKELVEY: At the expense
of convenience, we will
sometimes make, you know, people
walk

39:07.712 --> 39:12.617 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
further, make people walk
through a space in order to just
potentially have the opportunity

39:12.617 --> 39:17.655 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
