different things. Maybe there is
someone doing a whiskey tasting

39:17.655 --> 39:22.193 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
over there or there is a cold
brew thing here or there is
someone presenting on the screen

39:22.193 --> 39:25.730 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
over there. Maybe I will take a
minute and go check that out.

39:25.730 --> 39:31.069 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
PAUL SOLMAN: And so glass-walled
offices, festooned with funky
furniture, the inevitable

39:31.069 --> 39:37.642 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
