but the alcohol is to...

39:48.653 --> 39:49.153 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
MIGUEL MCKELVEY: Lubricate.

39:49.153 --> 39:49.454 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
PAUL SOLMAN: To lubricate.

39:49.454 --> 39:50.188 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(LAUGHTER)

39:50.188 --> 39:51.656 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
MIGUEL MCKELVEY: Yes.

39:51.656 --> 39:53.391 align:left position:25%,start line:86.67% size:75%
PAUL SOLMAN: To
lubricate community?

39:53.391 --> 39:56.160 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
MIGUEL MCKELVEY: Yes.

39:56.160 --> 40:02.166 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PAUL SOLMAN: WeWork isn't the
only firm housing the
