Greenwald, for us all.

41:23.948 --> 41:28.052 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
RICHARD GREENWALD: If we're
moving to this entrepreneurial
utopia, where everyone's their

41:28.052 --> 41:34.625 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
own boss, those who are lucky
