pattern continues.

41:39.464 --> 41:43.901 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
PAUL SOLMAN: But, for the
moment, WeWork tenants like Lily
Brynes embrace the new freelance

41:43.901 --> 41:46.170 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
economy.

41:46.170 --> 41:52.543 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Do you feel vulnerable being a
